WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:00.501 --> 00:00:04.221
No animals were harmed
or killed during the making of this film.

2
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

3
00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:22.780
Mother nature gives birth to all things.

4
00:00:24.141 --> 00:00:25.180
Summer season

5
00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:27.100
Rainy season

6
00:00:28.221 --> 00:00:29.421
Winter season

7
00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:33.621
And witching season.

8
00:00:36.140 --> 00:00:37.860
A season dreaded by all.

9
00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:41.060
It's the time when those who wield black magic

10
00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:43.940
unleash their powers to test their might.

11
00:00:44.660 --> 00:00:47.900
Those with bad luck may fall victim.

12
00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:50.740
- ending up cursed or worse.
- Close the shop! Go home!

13
00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:52.060
Hurry up! Leave now!

14
00:00:52.460 --> 00:00:54.620
I'll do your hair tomorrow. just leave!

15
00:00:55.060 --> 00:00:56.020
I'm closing the shop.

16
00:01:13.739 --> 00:01:15.580
The ominous wind drifts by

17
00:01:16.540 --> 00:01:18.460
like a whisper of death itself.

18
00:01:19.379 --> 00:01:20.900
Push. push. Nuan. push!

19
00:01:21.419 --> 00:01:25.059
And I was born on that day.

20
00:01:25.299 --> 00:01:26.420
Push. push. push!

21
00:01:27.140 --> 00:01:28.460
Yes. push. push!

22
00:01:28.539 --> 00:01:32.300
Yes. Nuan! Just a little more!

23
00:01:41.259 --> 00:01:42.299
Push now!

24
00:01:43.779 --> 00:01:45.620
It's coming out! It's coming out!

25
00:01:48.899 --> 00:01:49.579
Push!

26
00:01:50.739 --> 00:01:52.539
Coming out! Coming out! Coming out!

27
00:02:24.259 --> 00:02:25.138
You devil child!

28
00:02:54.259 --> 00:02:56.299
"9 years later"

29
00:02:56.938 --> 00:03:00.378
Wanna buy ducks? Chickens? Ducks?

30
00:03:01.378 --> 00:03:03.138
Ducks! Ducks!

31
00:03:06.858 --> 00:03:08.098
I know that one is old.

32
00:03:08.178 --> 00:03:09.858
These are fresh. I tell you.

33
00:03:10.298 --> 00:03:11.138
Thank you.

34
00:03:33.818 --> 00:03:35.097
What's your name?

35
00:03:37.338 --> 00:03:38.898
Alright. let me name you.

36
00:03:39.938 --> 00:03:42.698
From now on. your name will be Panor

37
00:03:43.098 --> 00:03:45.697
so people will love and adore you.

38
00:03:47.337 --> 00:03:48.378
Hold out your hand.

39
00:03:55.458 --> 00:03:57.177
May you be a good child.

40
00:03:58.737 --> 00:04:04.257
Live long. healthy and prosper.

41
00:04:08.137 --> 00:04:08.737
Father!

42
00:04:12.217 --> 00:04:13.017
Father!

43
00:04:13.097 --> 00:04:15.257
Abbot! Are you okay?

44
00:04:18.897 --> 00:04:21.337
Oh no. Abbot! I can't touch him.

45
00:04:22.217 --> 00:04:22.977
Father!

46
00:04:25.097 --> 00:04:25.817
Father!

47
00:04:26.657 --> 00:04:27.297
Father!

48
00:04:28.177 --> 00:04:31.497
Nuan. I told you not to bring
this devil child here.

49
00:04:31.577 --> 00:04:32.336
Father!

50
00:04:35.257 --> 00:04:35.857
Father!

51
00:04:36.577 --> 00:04:37.097
You jinx.

52
00:04:37.177 --> 00:04:38.417
What happened to him?

53
00:04:45.497 --> 00:04:47.456
PANOR

54
00:04:50.377 --> 00:04:51.577
"Grade 12"

55
00:05:01.697 --> 00:05:04.416
"Panor Boonsuk"

56
00:05:16.736 --> 00:05:18.256
Another round! Do it again!

57
00:05:18.336 --> 00:05:20.856
- Jump. jump!
- One. two. three!

58
00:05:23.416 --> 00:05:24.136
Right! Score!

59
00:05:25.136 --> 00:05:26.016
Bring it on!

60
00:05:28.176 --> 00:05:29.096
He's good!

61
00:05:29.176 --> 00:05:29.856
Left!

62
00:05:35.656 --> 00:05:38.056
You're the best. Pong!

63
00:05:40.216 --> 00:05:41.656
Come on. let's go again.

64
00:05:42.376 --> 00:05:43.536
Wow. so bold.

65
00:05:43.855 --> 00:05:46.975
Everyone in the school knows who Pong belongs to.

66
00:05:47.215 --> 00:05:48.216
She's such a slut.

67
00:05:50.935 --> 00:05:52.135
Want me to slap her. Jib?

68
00:05:53.496 --> 00:05:54.216
No need.

69
00:05:55.816 --> 00:05:57.336
Heading home. kids?

70
00:05:58.135 --> 00:05:59.976
Tuck your shirts in properly.

71
00:06:00.456 --> 00:06:01.456
Ten-minute break. drink some water.

72
00:06:01.536 --> 00:06:02.616
then we'll play again.

73
00:06:02.935 --> 00:06:04.096
Alright. thank you.

74
00:06:08.776 --> 00:06:10.816
Pong. here's your drink.

75
00:06:13.336 --> 00:06:15.095
Oh. the ground swallowed her up!

76
00:06:16.336 --> 00:06:17.776
A fallen angel. hm?

77
00:06:19.696 --> 00:06:20.455
Are you okay?

78
00:06:21.415 --> 00:06:22.336
Get up.

79
00:06:56.814 --> 00:06:57.654
What's up with her?

80
00:07:12.135 --> 00:07:12.855
What?

81
00:07:44.614 --> 00:07:47.734
Shit. go get the teacher. hurry!

82
00:08:02.774 --> 00:08:03.734
Stop scratching!

83
00:08:05.534 --> 00:08:06.413
What happened to her?

84
00:08:06.494 --> 00:08:06.974
I don't know.

85
00:08:08.333 --> 00:08:09.734
Take Chompoo to the infirmary.

86
00:08:16.534 --> 00:08:19.373
Why are you standing in the way. you jinx? Move!

87
00:08:28.133 --> 00:08:28.853
Go away!

88
00:08:48.134 --> 00:08:50.133
Here. iced black coffee!

89
00:08:50.213 --> 00:08:51.173
Thanks. uncle.

90
00:08:51.533 --> 00:08:52.773
Be careful. don't spill it.

91
00:08:52.853 --> 00:08:53.653
Alright.

92
00:08:53.733 --> 00:08:54.893
What would you like?

93
00:08:56.573 --> 00:08:57.373
Thanks a lot.

94
00:09:07.413 --> 00:09:09.533
For last week's steamed fish curry.

95
00:09:10.053 --> 00:09:10.813
Thank you. aunty.

96
00:09:10.893 --> 00:09:11.533
Yeah.

97
00:09:20.212 --> 00:09:21.493
You gave me too much.

98
00:09:21.573 --> 00:09:23.853
Keep it. Consider it a gift.

99
00:09:24.693 --> 00:09:25.453
Thank you.

100
00:09:25.533 --> 00:09:29.293
I think you should
make 2-3 more kinds of desserts.

101
00:09:29.373 --> 00:09:31.813
I'll help you sell them.

102
00:09:32.493 --> 00:09:33.133
Alright.

103
00:09:34.813 --> 00:09:36.292
Your mother is something else.

104
00:09:36.373 --> 00:09:37.693
She doesn't do anything all day.

105
00:09:38.332 --> 00:09:40.412
just leaves her kid to make a living.

106
00:09:40.933 --> 00:09:43.852
Are you finishing highschool this year?

107
00:09:44.332 --> 00:09:46.372
Have you decided what to study next?

108
00:09:47.332 --> 00:09:48.932
I'm going to take the exam to become a teacher.

109
00:09:49.012 --> 00:09:50.132
I want to be a teacher.

110
00:09:50.212 --> 00:09:51.973
Good. good.

111
00:09:52.093 --> 00:09:55.052
I think you'll do well.

112
00:09:55.132 --> 00:09:56.252
Study hard.

113
00:09:57.092 --> 00:09:58.772
I'll be going now. aunt Yam.

114
00:10:05.692 --> 00:10:07.172
Steamed fish curry!

115
00:10:07.932 --> 00:10:10.172
- Here you go
- Two packets.

116
00:10:10.252 --> 00:10:13.172
"Trisoon Photo"

117
00:10:19.852 --> 00:10:21.572
Transferring during mid year...

118
00:10:22.092 --> 00:10:24.291
must have been a hassle with all the paperwork.

119
00:10:25.611 --> 00:10:28.652
I'm used to it. My dad moves a lot.

120
00:10:29.292 --> 00:10:33.291
Well. if he's getting promoted. then it's worth.

121
00:10:36.771 --> 00:10:38.772
But you probably don't have many friends. right?

122
00:10:41.052 --> 00:10:42.291
It's done now.

123
00:10:46.412 --> 00:10:47.892
Your steamed fish curry. uncle Tri.

124
00:10:49.491 --> 00:10:50.931
Oh. Panor!

125
00:10:52.611 --> 00:10:54.492
Uncle. here is my friend.

126
00:11:12.291 --> 00:11:13.891
Aren't you going to smile for the photo?

127
00:11:16.291 --> 00:11:17.411
Why aren't you smiling?

128
00:11:17.611 --> 00:11:19.691
Like this. show your teeth! Smile!

129
00:11:20.411 --> 00:11:22.811
Yeah. Hands on your hips!

130
00:11:23.971 --> 00:11:25.211
Ready?

131
00:11:25.291 --> 00:11:26.091
Smile.

132
00:11:27.171 --> 00:11:29.811
Keep smiling... one... two...

133
00:11:30.211 --> 00:11:30.811
Three!

134
00:11:38.891 --> 00:11:39.451
Damn you!

135
00:11:40.571 --> 00:11:41.210
Where are you going?

136
00:12:04.451 --> 00:12:05.210
I give up!

137
00:12:06.491 --> 00:12:07.490
Give me the money!

138
00:12:15.491 --> 00:12:16.451
This is just the interest.

139
00:12:16.890 --> 00:12:18.930
Make sure to repay Mr. Kieng in full.

140
00:12:27.690 --> 00:12:28.730
Piak. watch out!

141
00:12:32.810 --> 00:12:33.570
Police!

142
00:12:34.250 --> 00:12:35.370
Police! Police!

143
00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:36.410
Police!

144
00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:38.130
Police! Police!

145
00:12:52.210 --> 00:12:53.329
Don't touch me!

146
00:12:56.089 --> 00:12:57.169
Wanna kill me?

147
00:12:58.129 --> 00:12:58.969
Kill me then!

148
00:13:00.289 --> 00:13:01.810
Just like you killed my mom!

149
00:13:23.050 --> 00:13:24.569
Devil child! Why are you here?

150
00:13:25.289 --> 00:13:28.529
Is Piak around? I brought desserts for him.

151
00:13:29.729 --> 00:13:32.369
I told you not to get near my son.

152
00:13:32.449 --> 00:13:33.969
Get out. you jinx! Go away!

153
00:14:11.369 --> 00:14:12.489
Panor!

154
00:14:13.289 --> 00:14:14.088
Panor!

155
00:14:14.769 --> 00:14:15.569
Go!

156
00:14:15.648 --> 00:14:17.409
Mom!

157
00:14:17.529 --> 00:14:19.488
Panor. what did you do to her?

158
00:14:20.848 --> 00:14:21.808
Mom! Mom!

159
00:14:21.888 --> 00:14:24.688
- Devil child. you killed my wife!
- Mom!

160
00:14:24.768 --> 00:14:26.649
Mom. what's wrong? Mom!

161
00:14:35.368 --> 00:14:37.008
That's why Piak hates me.

162
00:14:43.728 --> 00:14:45.208
Are you scared of me now?

163
00:14:45.848 --> 00:14:47.808
No. of course not.

164
00:14:48.728 --> 00:14:49.808
Who would ever?

165
00:14:50.568 --> 00:14:52.248
Let them think what they want.

166
00:14:52.328 --> 00:14:55.368
I'm lucky to be friends with a witch.

167
00:14:59.408 --> 00:15:03.008
Panor. I saw Piak get stabbed. but he wasn't hurt.

168
00:15:03.568 --> 00:15:04.848
Does Piak use black magic too?

169
00:15:12.928 --> 00:15:15.368
Here. take it. I'm not eating it.

170
00:16:19.966 --> 00:16:22.327
(Chanting)

171
00:16:22.407 --> 00:16:24.166
(Chanting)

172
00:16:25.047 --> 00:16:26.887
(Chanting)

173
00:16:27.567 --> 00:16:29.007
(Chanting)

174
00:16:29.566 --> 00:16:32.767
(Chanting)

175
00:16:35.527 --> 00:16:38.767
Like someone about to drown

176
00:16:39.926 --> 00:16:46.406
♪ Struggling desperately to swim to the shore ♪

177
00:16:48.566 --> 00:16:53.287
♪ If you don't shun the broken-hearted ♪

178
00:16:53.726 --> 00:16:56.966
♪ Please lift the fallen ♪

179
00:16:57.086 --> 00:17:01.366
♪ pull me to the shore of your heart ♪

180
00:17:02.006 --> 00:17:08.246
♪ I feel like I'm drifting.
drifting amidst a sea of tears ♪

181
00:17:08.766 --> 00:17:12.926
♪ Hoping the sky will have mercy ♪

182
00:17:13.006 --> 00:17:15.846
♪ Let me survive ♪

183
00:17:16.566 --> 00:17:19.646
♪ If there's true love... ♪

184
00:17:43.365 --> 00:17:45.366
I'll be with you soon. my child.

185
00:17:59.605 --> 00:18:00.685
What are you doing. Mom?

186
00:18:01.125 --> 00:18:03.205
Please don't do this. I'm begging you.

187
00:18:03.325 --> 00:18:04.206
Let go of me.

188
00:18:08.685 --> 00:18:09.685
Let go of me.

189
00:20:35.563 --> 00:20:37.323
Whose body? Who is he?

190
00:20:47.083 --> 00:20:48.283
This guy's name is Tos. Inspector.

191
00:20:49.323 --> 00:20:50.963
He sells fish at the market.

192
00:20:52.083 --> 00:20:54.203
He's been fishing since he was a kid.

193
00:20:54.643 --> 00:20:56.963
Judging by the state of the body. he didn't drown.

194
00:20:57.483 --> 00:20:59.603
Aum. do you know anything about this?

195
00:20:59.802 --> 00:21:03.003
Last night. I was just drinking with him as usual.

196
00:21:03.923 --> 00:21:07.403
Before he left. he said
he'd go fishing near Nuan's house.

197
00:21:08.603 --> 00:21:09.563
Nuan's house?

198
00:21:15.203 --> 00:21:15.963
Oh?

199
00:21:24.402 --> 00:21:25.162
Inspector!

200
00:21:25.282 --> 00:21:26.043
Inspector!

201
00:21:26.523 --> 00:21:27.562
Look at this.

202
00:21:29.962 --> 00:21:32.322
I think Tos definitely was cursed.

203
00:21:35.602 --> 00:21:38.643
Panor. you killed my husband. huh?!

204
00:21:38.722 --> 00:21:40.803
Panor!

205
00:21:41.002 --> 00:21:41.922
You wicked!

206
00:21:42.003 --> 00:21:43.242
You killed my husband!

207
00:21:43.602 --> 00:21:44.762
I'm gonna kill you!

208
00:21:45.202 --> 00:21:46.162
Panor!

209
00:21:46.602 --> 00:21:48.882
Panor! I'm gonna kill you!

210
00:21:49.242 --> 00:21:50.282
You wicked girl!

211
00:21:56.122 --> 00:21:57.042
Let's sit here.

212
00:22:02.362 --> 00:22:03.962
Everyone's crazy here.

213
00:22:05.002 --> 00:22:06.722
How can they suddenly accuse you?

214
00:22:08.522 --> 00:22:11.362
That guy really looked like he was cursed. Taew.

215
00:22:12.041 --> 00:22:15.002
What did you find out. Panor? Tell me.

216
00:22:16.882 --> 00:22:20.762
I dreamed that I followed a man
to an abandoned temple.

217
00:22:21.562 --> 00:22:23.801
He had the same tattoo as that body.

218
00:22:24.761 --> 00:22:26.482
Did you see his face?

219
00:22:28.001 --> 00:22:30.482
No. but I remember the tattoo.

220
00:22:31.041 --> 00:22:32.402
Can you draw it?

221
00:22:56.321 --> 00:22:57.881
How about we go to the abandoned temple?

222
00:22:57.961 --> 00:23:00.161
If we find anything. I can show it to my dad.

223
00:23:01.761 --> 00:23:02.761
Come on. let's go.

224
00:23:07.721 --> 00:23:08.401
Ow.

225
00:23:08.961 --> 00:23:09.801
What's wrong?

226
00:23:14.401 --> 00:23:15.081
Oh?

227
00:23:32.401 --> 00:23:34.480
It looks very painful.

228
00:23:35.800 --> 00:23:38.320
Is it usually this bad?

229
00:23:38.841 --> 00:23:40.360
This never happened before.

230
00:23:40.441 --> 00:23:42.601
What? Is this your first period?

231
00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:51.601
Thanks.

232
00:23:51.680 --> 00:23:52.840
Do you know how to use it?

233
00:23:53.761 --> 00:23:54.640
I'll try.

234
00:23:55.681 --> 00:23:57.200
Is your stomach still hurting?

235
00:23:59.360 --> 00:24:01.600
Wait here. I'll go buy some painkiller.

236
00:24:03.280 --> 00:24:05.320
Auntie. can you watch Panor? I'll go get medicine.

237
00:24:05.400 --> 00:24:06.280
Sure. sure.

238
00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:07.920
What are you even doing here?

239
00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:09.880
Go. this has nothing to do with men. Go.

240
00:24:10.240 --> 00:24:13.280
- It's women's stuff.
- But it's exciting. Panor's now a woman.

241
00:24:20.760 --> 00:24:21.400
Taew.

242
00:24:22.840 --> 00:24:24.120
- Yes?
- What are you doing here?

243
00:24:25.040 --> 00:24:26.320
Talk later. Dad. I'm in a hurry.

244
00:24:27.920 --> 00:24:28.920
- Let's go. sarge.
- Yes. sir.

245
00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:36.120
Sorry. sir.

246
00:25:06.840 --> 00:25:07.839
I need to get going.

247
00:25:34.199 --> 00:25:40.358
(Chanting)

248
00:26:32.238 --> 00:26:33.278
Taew! Taew!

249
00:26:33.358 --> 00:26:34.398
Taew. what's wrong?

250
00:26:34.638 --> 00:26:36.118
Taew. Taew. Taew!

251
00:26:36.678 --> 00:26:38.438
Panor. help me!

252
00:26:40.438 --> 00:26:44.118
Panor. I found the man with the tattoo!

253
00:26:44.318 --> 00:26:45.358
Taew!

254
00:26:53.838 --> 00:26:54.678
Taew!

255
00:26:54.838 --> 00:26:56.358
Taew. Taew. Taew!

256
00:26:59.358 --> 00:27:00.438
Taew! Taew!

257
00:27:12.718 --> 00:27:14.197
Taew. Taew. Taew!

258
00:27:21.157 --> 00:27:22.037
Sarge. pull over.

259
00:27:23.557 --> 00:27:24.598
I heard someone scream.

260
00:27:25.597 --> 00:27:26.317
Taew!

261
00:27:31.877 --> 00:27:32.957
Taew!

262
00:27:39.837 --> 00:27:42.077
Taew. Taew. Taew!

263
00:27:45.357 --> 00:27:45.997
Taew!

264
00:27:49.797 --> 00:27:51.197
Taew. Taew!

265
00:27:51.357 --> 00:27:52.157
What are you doing?

266
00:27:53.277 --> 00:27:54.037
What's going on?

267
00:27:54.637 --> 00:27:55.797
Taew!

268
00:27:56.157 --> 00:27:56.797
Taew!

269
00:27:57.797 --> 00:27:58.837
Taew. Taew!

270
00:28:00.996 --> 00:28:02.757
Panor! Let go of my girl!

271
00:28:03.837 --> 00:28:06.156
Let go! If you don't. I'll shoot!

272
00:28:06.437 --> 00:28:07.596
Inspector. she's just a kid.

273
00:28:08.196 --> 00:28:08.957
Go get her.

274
00:28:10.317 --> 00:28:11.037
Taew!

275
00:28:12.156 --> 00:28:12.756
Taew!

276
00:28:13.677 --> 00:28:14.637
Taew. Taew!

277
00:28:15.516 --> 00:28:16.077
Taew!

278
00:28:16.157 --> 00:28:18.677
Let go! I'm trying to help Taew!

279
00:28:26.116 --> 00:28:27.916
What's the cause of death. doctor?

280
00:28:30.597 --> 00:28:33.117
Your daughter died from massive blood loss.

281
00:28:35.277 --> 00:28:37.836
Her body suffered severe lacerations.

282
00:28:40.317 --> 00:28:42.636
Starting from the throat. esophagus.

283
00:28:43.876 --> 00:28:46.676
stomach. intestines.

284
00:28:50.276 --> 00:28:51.356
all the way to the vaginal area.

285
00:28:52.916 --> 00:28:54.836
Did you find any weapon at the scene. sir?

286
00:28:57.396 --> 00:29:00.636
I only saw the girl. Panor. choking my daughter.

287
00:29:03.836 --> 00:29:07.236
What kind of weapon could cause such injuries?

288
00:29:36.116 --> 00:29:37.115
Get out of there.

289
00:29:44.475 --> 00:29:46.035
I didn't kill Taew.

290
00:29:48.596 --> 00:29:50.315
I was trying to save her.

291
00:29:51.236 --> 00:29:53.876
Leave before I change my mind.

292
00:30:08.195 --> 00:30:10.355
Why are you letting her go so easily. sir?

293
00:30:10.435 --> 00:30:12.795
We don't have evidence against her yet.

294
00:30:13.515 --> 00:30:16.435
But if it turns out to be true.
I won't let it slide.

295
00:30:19.075 --> 00:30:20.075
Come here!

296
00:30:20.715 --> 00:30:22.555
I sent you to school.
all you do is cause problems!

297
00:30:22.635 --> 00:30:23.635
Damn curse!

298
00:30:25.155 --> 00:30:26.794
I didn't kill Taew!

299
00:30:27.034 --> 00:30:28.915
The tattooed man did it!

300
00:30:29.355 --> 00:30:30.795
Don't get involved with anyone.

301
00:30:31.515 --> 00:30:32.875
if you don't want to see them die.

302
00:30:34.875 --> 00:30:35.554
Mom!

303
00:30:35.755 --> 00:30:36.475
Mom!

304
00:30:36.754 --> 00:30:37.635
Mom!

305
00:30:38.035 --> 00:30:39.394
Mom. open the door!

306
00:30:41.715 --> 00:30:44.194
"Your daughter started her period. It's time."

307
00:30:44.275 --> 00:30:45.994
"Take care of her."

308
00:31:12.714 --> 00:31:13.594
Mom!

309
00:31:14.074 --> 00:31:16.634
Mom. I heard something.

310
00:31:17.194 --> 00:31:17.994
Mom!

311
00:31:19.394 --> 00:31:21.114
What's that chant. Mom?

312
00:33:44.472 --> 00:33:45.112
Old Yim!

313
00:34:19.751 --> 00:34:22.792
"Grade 12"

314
00:34:22.871 --> 00:34:25.231
- Have you heard about Taew yet?
- What happened?

315
00:34:25.312 --> 00:34:26.551
Her body is horrifying.

316
00:34:26.632 --> 00:34:29.711
Her whole body. arms.
and legs were covered in wounds.

317
00:34:29.791 --> 00:34:31.751
Blood everywhere.
Just thinking about it gives me chills.

318
00:34:36.791 --> 00:34:37.871
Curly?

319
00:34:38.151 --> 00:34:39.111
Is it Curly?

320
00:34:39.751 --> 00:34:40.831
What did she do?

321
00:35:36.150 --> 00:35:37.470
Don't you worry. Taew.

322
00:35:39.111 --> 00:35:40.710
Whoever it is.

323
00:35:41.991 --> 00:35:44.391
I'll drag him out and make him pay.

324
00:35:52.910 --> 00:35:54.110
She's gorgeous.

325
00:35:54.190 --> 00:35:56.270
She's like an angel.

326
00:35:57.230 --> 00:35:58.230
She's pretty.

327
00:35:59.430 --> 00:36:01.430
You don't need to do school chores.

328
00:36:03.830 --> 00:36:07.110
Don't you know boys are crazy about you now?

329
00:36:07.990 --> 00:36:11.150
You can boss them around all you want.

330
00:36:16.829 --> 00:36:17.470
Then...

331
00:36:19.270 --> 00:36:20.630
Can you do something for me. Pong?

332
00:36:22.349 --> 00:36:23.030
Sure.

333
00:36:23.429 --> 00:36:24.989
What do you need?

334
00:36:53.309 --> 00:36:57.230
I heard there used to be a temple on this island.

335
00:36:58.749 --> 00:37:00.629
But every monk who stayed there died.

336
00:37:02.069 --> 00:37:03.469
So. it's abandoned.

337
00:37:24.748 --> 00:37:26.029
It's not abandoned.

338
00:37:26.869 --> 00:37:28.509
People still come here.

339
00:37:46.868 --> 00:37:47.548
Jib.

340
00:37:48.068 --> 00:37:49.268
Thank you. Pong.

341
00:37:49.828 --> 00:37:52.268
I believe now that you really love me.

342
00:37:57.349 --> 00:37:59.788
You were talking to Panor. Do you like her?

343
00:38:01.628 --> 00:38:04.388
No. why would I like her?

344
00:38:06.949 --> 00:38:07.708
Prove it.

345
00:38:14.428 --> 00:38:15.868
I've done as I promised.

346
00:38:17.028 --> 00:38:18.948
Don't forget to tell your dad
to clear my family's debt.

347
00:38:20.788 --> 00:38:21.428
Sure.

348
00:38:25.868 --> 00:38:26.828
Where are you going?

349
00:38:26.908 --> 00:38:27.708
Come here.

350
00:38:27.788 --> 00:38:28.788
Let me go!

351
00:38:28.868 --> 00:38:29.628
Where are you going?

352
00:38:29.708 --> 00:38:30.668
- Come here.
- Come here!

353
00:38:30.748 --> 00:38:31.468
Let go!

354
00:38:31.908 --> 00:38:32.508
Come here.

355
00:38:32.868 --> 00:38:33.628
Let go!

356
00:38:34.148 --> 00:38:34.947
Sit quietly.

357
00:38:38.028 --> 00:38:39.228
Grab her. come on!

358
00:38:39.627 --> 00:38:40.428
Why are you resisting?

359
00:38:40.508 --> 00:38:42.068
- Get off of me!
- Stay still!

360
00:38:42.147 --> 00:38:43.308
Let go! Let go!

361
00:38:46.548 --> 00:38:47.508
So strong. huh?

362
00:38:48.027 --> 00:38:49.148
Nue. come help!

363
00:38:57.987 --> 00:38:58.668
Hey!

364
00:39:00.147 --> 00:39:00.787
Who the fuck?

365
00:39:00.867 --> 00:39:01.548
Piak

366
00:39:25.747 --> 00:39:26.267
Pong

367
00:39:26.347 --> 00:39:28.227
Pong. are you okay? Pong.

368
00:39:34.667 --> 00:39:35.347
Pong

369
00:39:46.267 --> 00:39:48.506
You were talking to Panor. Do you like her?

370
00:39:50.666 --> 00:39:51.347
No.

371
00:39:53.546 --> 00:39:54.986
why would I like her?

372
00:39:56.827 --> 00:39:57.667
Prove it.

373
00:40:01.507 --> 00:40:02.507
Thank you.

374
00:40:03.266 --> 00:40:04.787
Don't think I'm being nice to you.

375
00:40:04.867 --> 00:40:07.307
The only one who can torment you is me.

376
00:40:14.546 --> 00:40:16.226
Stand up for yourself.
Stop letting them bully you.

377
00:40:16.907 --> 00:40:18.266
If you don't want to be bullied...

378
00:40:18.347 --> 00:40:20.306
make it so no one dares to mess with you.

379
00:40:30.666 --> 00:40:32.586
Piak beat us up good.

380
00:40:32.666 --> 00:40:34.386
Damn. now he knows how to fight.

381
00:40:41.826 --> 00:40:42.866
What the fuck?

382
00:40:46.226 --> 00:40:47.706
What's got into you. Panor?

383
00:40:52.746 --> 00:40:53.746
Fuck off!

384
00:41:10.825 --> 00:41:11.466
No!

385
00:41:40.505 --> 00:41:42.185
I hurt some people at school.

386
00:41:43.825 --> 00:41:45.025
I've tried...

387
00:41:49.985 --> 00:41:51.665
But I couldn't control myself.

388
00:42:02.385 --> 00:42:06.504
At least you didn't do anything worse.

389
00:42:07.985 --> 00:42:09.585
Forgive them. will you?

390
00:42:33.945 --> 00:42:36.984
The control totem is strong this time. Father.

391
00:42:38.344 --> 00:42:39.624
Please endure it.

392
00:43:04.944 --> 00:43:08.864
(A prayer)

393
00:44:31.383 --> 00:44:42.703
(Chanting)

394
00:45:04.543 --> 00:45:12.622
(Chanting)

395
00:47:21.461 --> 00:47:26.460
(Chanting)

396
00:47:27.260 --> 00:47:32.700
(Chanting)

397
00:47:47.900 --> 00:47:48.540
Uncle Tri.

398
00:47:58.699 --> 00:48:04.060
(Chanting)

399
00:49:13.899 --> 00:49:15.219
You're safe now. Panor.

400
00:49:24.099 --> 00:49:27.059
I told you to take care of her. And you couldn't!

401
00:49:29.178 --> 00:49:29.898
Mom!

402
00:49:32.338 --> 00:49:33.258
Take this!

403
00:49:33.579 --> 00:49:34.738
Take this!

404
00:49:35.458 --> 00:49:36.579
Damn it!

405
00:49:37.338 --> 00:49:38.658
Why are you hurting my mother?

406
00:49:40.138 --> 00:49:41.098
Your mother?

407
00:49:41.938 --> 00:49:44.058
She doesn't think of herself
as your mother. Panor.

408
00:49:45.738 --> 00:49:48.378
She was just hired to give birth to you. you fool.

409
00:50:00.338 --> 00:50:03.298
Your job here is done. Get the fuck out of here.

410
00:50:07.498 --> 00:50:08.298
Go!

411
00:50:24.098 --> 00:50:24.778
Mom.

412
00:50:28.097 --> 00:50:28.738
Mom.

413
00:50:34.097 --> 00:50:35.858
It's your turn to take over your mother's duties.

414
00:50:48.338 --> 00:50:50.177
You've wasted 18 years of my life. Panor.

415
00:50:54.338 --> 00:50:55.298
Let me go.

416
00:51:01.217 --> 00:51:03.577
You... You're the one who killed Taew!

417
00:51:05.177 --> 00:51:07.457
You're why Taew died.

418
00:51:09.897 --> 00:51:10.777
Let go!

419
00:51:15.337 --> 00:51:16.177
Come with me.

420
00:51:53.456 --> 00:51:55.216
Mom. what's this all about?

421
00:51:56.096 --> 00:51:57.416
Don't ask right now.

422
00:52:14.576 --> 00:52:15.736
Panor. get down.

423
00:52:27.376 --> 00:52:28.496
Panor. down!

424
00:52:29.816 --> 00:52:30.496
Ah!

425
00:52:33.216 --> 00:52:33.896
Mom!

426
00:52:34.536 --> 00:52:36.176
Ow! Ow!

427
00:52:37.816 --> 00:52:38.496
Mom!

428
00:52:42.336 --> 00:52:43.215
Get away!

429
00:53:03.175 --> 00:53:03.975
Get away!

430
00:53:05.616 --> 00:53:06.255
Mom!

431
00:53:47.935 --> 00:53:49.215
Help us!

432
00:53:50.815 --> 00:53:51.575
Help!

433
00:53:56.534 --> 00:53:59.135
Mom. mom. mom. hurry!

434
00:54:00.215 --> 00:54:00.974
Mom!

435
00:54:01.094 --> 00:54:01.814
Nuan.

436
00:54:02.294 --> 00:54:02.975
Nuan.

437
00:54:05.335 --> 00:54:05.894
Nuan.

438
00:54:05.975 --> 00:54:06.614
Mom!

439
00:54:11.095 --> 00:54:13.014
Please take care of my child.

440
00:54:19.934 --> 00:54:23.814
I'm sorry. my child.

441
00:54:28.454 --> 00:54:29.975
Mom! Mom!

442
00:54:30.095 --> 00:54:32.654
Mom! Mom!

443
00:55:15.133 --> 00:55:15.694
Oi!

444
00:55:18.214 --> 00:55:20.614
Hey. Piak. what are you doing here?

445
00:55:20.694 --> 00:55:21.814
What are you doing here. sarge?

446
00:55:21.894 --> 00:55:23.053
What's with you?

447
00:55:23.453 --> 00:55:26.533
The whole market is in chaos now. Pla is dead.

448
00:55:26.893 --> 00:55:30.694
That Jib girl is making a ruckus
that Panor cursed Pla.

449
00:55:38.813 --> 00:55:40.813
Sarge. search throughly.

450
00:55:41.173 --> 00:55:41.813
Yes. sir.

451
00:55:55.293 --> 00:55:55.813
Sarge.

452
00:55:55.893 --> 00:55:57.133
Nothing's in the room.

453
00:56:01.773 --> 00:56:03.013
- Upstairs.
- Yes. sir.

454
00:56:20.052 --> 00:56:21.132
What the hell is this?

455
00:56:35.292 --> 00:56:35.973
Sarge.

456
00:56:36.252 --> 00:56:36.892
Yes. sir.

457
00:56:39.012 --> 00:56:39.732
Damn!

458
00:57:06.652 --> 00:57:07.532
He said...

459
00:57:08.692 --> 00:57:10.572
Mom was hired to carry me.

460
00:57:15.212 --> 00:57:17.132
What does that mean. Auntie?

461
00:57:29.372 --> 00:57:30.332
There it goes.

462
00:57:31.451 --> 00:57:33.052
What's all this about. Abbot?

463
00:57:40.571 --> 00:57:42.092
Nuan wanted to be a singer.

464
00:57:42.851 --> 00:57:44.372
But Pa and Ma wouldn't have it.

465
00:57:44.651 --> 00:57:45.812
so she ran away from home.

466
00:57:46.731 --> 00:57:50.651
She planned to move to Bangkok
to follow her dream.

467
00:57:51.651 --> 00:57:53.012
Until one day...

468
00:57:54.851 --> 00:57:56.732
She encountered those cultists.

469
00:57:57.692 --> 00:57:59.531
They offered her a large sum of money

470
00:58:00.291 --> 00:58:01.251
to...

471
00:58:03.531 --> 00:58:05.051
carry a child.

472
00:58:25.091 --> 00:58:27.291
Some black magic cults

473
00:58:27.691 --> 00:58:31.731
have a way to preserve their powers from fading

474
00:58:32.851 --> 00:58:35.131
by storing them in a woman's womb.

475
00:58:36.010 --> 00:58:41.050
so the child born would inherit their magic.

476
00:58:43.251 --> 00:58:46.131
The child corpse must have been...

477
00:58:46.570 --> 00:58:49.930
drained by Panor while they were in the womb.

478
00:58:50.571 --> 00:58:53.770
All the magic. therefore. remains within Panor.

479
00:58:58.730 --> 00:59:00.850
Nuan wrote letters to me for a while.

480
00:59:02.570 --> 00:59:04.130
You can read them yourself.

481
00:59:29.210 --> 00:59:30.690
My life is over.

482
00:59:32.090 --> 00:59:35.450
The child they wanted... died in the womb.

483
00:59:36.770 --> 00:59:38.210
I can't go anywhere

484
00:59:39.090 --> 00:59:40.250
until I raise another child

485
00:59:40.330 --> 00:59:42.450
to be old enough to have a child for them.

486
00:59:43.689 --> 00:59:44.889
What should I do?

487
00:59:46.850 --> 00:59:48.530
Ever since that cursed one was born...

488
00:59:49.610 --> 00:59:51.330
my life has been nothing but misery.

489
00:59:55.970 --> 00:59:57.849
It was born to ruin my life.

490
00:59:58.569 --> 01:00:00.090
I hate her. Ni.

491
01:00:01.130 --> 01:00:02.730
I've never thought of her as my child.

492
01:00:05.889 --> 01:00:06.930
But you know?

493
01:00:08.130 --> 01:00:09.810
No matter how cruel I am to her.

494
01:00:10.890 --> 01:00:12.369
she never complains.

495
01:00:13.729 --> 01:00:14.809
She loves me

496
01:00:15.690 --> 01:00:17.130
and never leaves me.

497
01:00:23.250 --> 01:00:25.410
Every time I see she studying hard.

498
01:00:25.729 --> 01:00:27.409
I feel so guilty toward her.

499
01:00:32.289 --> 01:00:36.089
Does she know how terrible the future will be?

500
01:00:37.609 --> 01:00:39.649
After everything I've done to her. Ni.

501
01:00:40.449 --> 01:00:41.769
Should I hate her

502
01:00:42.489 --> 01:00:43.569
or love her?

503
01:00:49.489 --> 01:00:50.889
I'm sorry. my child.

504
01:00:55.529 --> 01:00:57.649
Mom. mom. mom. mom!

505
01:00:57.728 --> 01:01:01.249
Mom. mom. mom!

506
01:01:13.969 --> 01:01:20.009
(Chanting)

507
01:01:33.848 --> 01:01:34.688
Come here.

508
01:01:52.968 --> 01:01:53.728
Panor!

509
01:01:55.688 --> 01:01:57.408
Panor! Panor. girl.

510
01:02:03.487 --> 01:02:04.807
Hold on. Panor.

511
01:02:05.647 --> 01:02:07.528
They're trying to pull it back.

512
01:02:08.167 --> 01:02:09.127
Stay strong. my child!

513
01:02:20.328 --> 01:02:24.168
(Chanting)

514
01:02:25.487 --> 01:02:26.567
Let it go!

515
01:02:29.167 --> 01:02:30.407
Panor! No!

516
01:02:36.967 --> 01:02:38.167
You dare fight me?

517
01:02:40.687 --> 01:02:41.767
Let it go!

518
01:02:44.887 --> 01:02:47.047
No! Don't do this!

519
01:02:47.967 --> 01:02:49.327
Ma. help me!

520
01:02:49.407 --> 01:02:51.807
- Stay strong!
- Help me!

521
01:02:59.647 --> 01:03:01.407
The only way to save you...

522
01:03:02.127 --> 01:03:04.287
You have to unleash the power within you.

523
01:03:05.007 --> 01:03:06.167
But remember this...

524
01:03:07.487 --> 01:03:09.767
The power will stay with you
until the day you die.

525
01:03:13.047 --> 01:03:20.087
(Chanting)

526
01:03:22.326 --> 01:03:23.807
Are you fighting me?

527
01:03:25.007 --> 01:03:25.806
Come!

528
01:03:26.207 --> 01:03:30.726
(Chanting)

529
01:03:39.526 --> 01:03:40.407
Taew!

530
01:03:43.767 --> 01:03:45.846
You want me to become a demon!

531
01:03:46.326 --> 01:03:49.047
Then I'll become a demon!

532
01:04:05.886 --> 01:04:08.006
Panor!

533
01:04:16.486 --> 01:04:17.286
Father...

534
01:04:18.086 --> 01:04:20.206
What did Panor do to you?

535
01:04:21.446 --> 01:04:24.206
Panor can extract curses from others

536
01:04:25.046 --> 01:04:26.566
and contain them within herself.

537
01:04:27.206 --> 01:04:29.006
When she realized she had this ability.

538
01:04:29.285 --> 01:04:31.366
she kept secretly helping me.

539
01:04:33.446 --> 01:04:35.006
On the day your mother died.

540
01:04:35.326 --> 01:04:39.005
Panor was actually trying to save her.

541
01:04:45.926 --> 01:04:49.805
Every time Panor pulls something
out of someone else

542
01:04:49.886 --> 01:04:51.405
and keeps it within herself.

543
01:04:51.485 --> 01:04:55.005
it is excruciatingly painful.
but she never tells anyone.

544
01:04:55.725 --> 01:04:57.926
Panor. get off!

545
01:04:58.046 --> 01:04:59.925
Mom!

546
01:05:00.645 --> 01:05:05.486
I never knew how the love potion
that I secretly made...

547
01:05:06.125 --> 01:05:09.605
- ...ended up with your mom.
- Desire my flesh. yearn for me.

548
01:05:09.845 --> 01:05:11.005
Caress my soul.

549
01:05:11.605 --> 01:05:12.965
Why didn't you tell me. dad?

550
01:05:14.925 --> 01:05:15.885
I was scared.

551
01:05:22.045 --> 01:05:23.485
I'm sorry. son.

552
01:05:36.484 --> 01:05:37.405
Thank you.

553
01:05:38.245 --> 01:05:39.805
Don't think I'm being nice to you.

554
01:05:41.085 --> 01:05:43.885
The only one who can torment you is me.

555
01:05:58.525 --> 01:05:59.684
Where are you going?

556
01:06:03.164 --> 01:06:06.124
I'll hunt down Panor. We've underestimated her.

557
01:06:07.084 --> 01:06:08.725
She's awakened the third eye now.

558
01:06:09.805 --> 01:06:14.365
Before. she didn't know how to use her magic.

559
01:06:15.604 --> 01:06:18.724
I won't let her keep what we entrusted to her.

560
01:06:19.244 --> 01:06:21.964
No. You stay here.

561
01:06:22.884 --> 01:06:26.644
Right now. her magic is unstable.

562
01:06:27.284 --> 01:06:30.364
Soon. she'll come to you herself.

563
01:06:51.324 --> 01:06:53.763
(Chanting)

564
01:07:03.884 --> 01:07:07.164
(Chanting)

565
01:07:07.243 --> 01:07:10.563
(Chanting)

566
01:07:12.483 --> 01:07:15.924
(Chanting)

567
01:07:31.043 --> 01:07:32.603
Can you stay a little longer?

568
01:07:33.443 --> 01:07:35.243
Dad rarely comes home late.

569
01:07:35.563 --> 01:07:37.243
Don't rush back just yet.

570
01:07:49.603 --> 01:07:50.723
Why so quiet?

571
01:07:54.003 --> 01:07:55.243
Are you thinking about Panor?

572
01:07:59.083 --> 01:08:00.443
You're being so jealous.

573
01:08:03.083 --> 01:08:05.923
I told you I don't like her.

574
01:08:07.322 --> 01:08:08.402
You know that. Jib.

575
01:08:14.963 --> 01:08:16.082
Don't overthink it.

576
01:08:17.363 --> 01:08:18.162
You aren't. right?

577
01:08:25.082 --> 01:08:26.363
Pong

578
01:08:26.802 --> 01:08:28.283
Have you heard the rumors?

579
01:08:29.562 --> 01:08:31.362
That she fought with her mom.

580
01:08:31.682 --> 01:08:33.203
They said the place was swimming with blood.

581
01:08:33.803 --> 01:08:34.802
I think they're right.

582
01:08:35.762 --> 01:08:36.402
Why?

583
01:08:37.682 --> 01:08:38.522
You miss her?

584
01:08:39.002 --> 01:08:39.842
Are you crazy?

585
01:08:40.562 --> 01:08:41.602
Who would miss her?

586
01:08:42.002 --> 01:08:43.402
It's good that she's gone.

587
01:08:44.322 --> 01:08:45.642
If she comes back.

588
01:08:46.522 --> 01:08:47.402
she's in for trouble.

589
01:08:48.362 --> 01:08:49.602
Aren't you afraid of her?

590
01:08:50.722 --> 01:08:51.882
She uses dark magic.

591
01:08:54.602 --> 01:08:55.682
I'm not afraid.

592
01:08:57.162 --> 01:08:58.122
I have the good stuff.

593
01:09:10.561 --> 01:09:11.722
Black dog's blood

594
01:09:12.282 --> 01:09:13.402
to break curses.

595
01:09:14.242 --> 01:09:15.601
You're so resourceful.

596
01:09:16.801 --> 01:09:17.521
Alright.

597
01:09:18.042 --> 01:09:19.282
I need to head home.

598
01:09:20.682 --> 01:09:21.481
Yeah.

599
01:09:25.762 --> 01:09:26.401
Go.

600
01:09:36.601 --> 01:09:37.522
I'm going.

601
01:09:38.962 --> 01:09:39.841
See you later.

602
01:09:50.401 --> 01:09:51.201
Panor!

603
01:09:55.001 --> 01:09:56.561
You do miss me. don't you?

604
01:09:57.841 --> 01:09:58.921
Well. here I am.

605
01:10:13.721 --> 01:10:17.520
(Chanting)

606
01:10:20.961 --> 01:10:24.720
(Chanting)

607
01:10:35.481 --> 01:10:37.161
It's Pla's ashes.

608
01:10:53.440 --> 01:10:54.441
Why scared?

609
01:10:55.560 --> 01:10:57.640
Isn't she your personal hairstylist?

610
01:11:05.120 --> 01:11:10.400
(Chanting)

611
01:11:22.000 --> 01:11:23.640
You already have Jib. don't you?

612
01:11:24.560 --> 01:11:26.440
This's the village chief's daughter.
and just moved in.

613
01:11:28.240 --> 01:11:29.960
She's incredibly beautiful.

614
01:11:30.440 --> 01:11:31.760
How could I let her slip through my fingers?

615
01:11:32.879 --> 01:11:34.400
You're aiming high.

616
01:11:41.639 --> 01:11:47.279
(Chanting)

617
01:11:50.439 --> 01:11:51.999
The "Horse Courting Maiden" yantra.

618
01:11:52.959 --> 01:11:54.639
...is the ultimate in love magic.

619
01:11:55.520 --> 01:11:57.479
But it's pricey. alright?

620
01:11:58.319 --> 01:11:59.840
I'll spare no expense.

621
01:12:01.799 --> 01:12:06.560
(Chanting)

622
01:12:25.879 --> 01:12:26.639
Fine!

623
01:12:33.039 --> 01:12:34.279
Uncle. wait for me.

624
01:13:11.959 --> 01:13:13.039
You're smart.

625
01:13:14.678 --> 01:13:15.718
fast learner.

626
01:13:16.718 --> 01:13:19.078
but beating me is another story.

627
01:14:06.198 --> 01:14:09.597
How dare you use my own spells against me. Panor?

628
01:14:09.678 --> 01:14:11.277
You killed my mother.

629
01:14:11.358 --> 01:14:12.877
You killed my friend.

630
01:14:13.717 --> 01:14:15.397
If anyone's going to kill you. it's me.

631
01:14:15.477 --> 01:14:16.837
After I extract the magic.

632
01:14:16.957 --> 01:14:18.957
you'll suffer worse than your mother!

633
01:15:00.437 --> 01:15:03.037
Using cloaking magic on me. Panor?

634
01:15:28.436 --> 01:15:29.477
Black dog's blood?

635
01:15:30.156 --> 01:15:30.797
Bitch!

636
01:16:08.716 --> 01:16:11.995
You've been doing this vile stuff
for a long time. haven't you?

637
01:16:23.916 --> 01:16:25.156
Who's this kid?

638
01:16:26.596 --> 01:16:29.755
He's your damn father. Panor.

639
01:16:34.276 --> 01:16:35.116
Father?

640
01:16:37.276 --> 01:16:39.715
The one who turned me into a demon?

641
01:17:20.274 --> 01:17:20.915
Pong...

642
01:17:27.594 --> 01:17:28.755
I love you. Pong.

643
01:17:29.634 --> 01:17:30.915
Don't leave me. Pong.

644
01:17:31.355 --> 01:17:32.675
Don't leave me. Pong.

645
01:17:33.474 --> 01:17:34.155
Pong.

646
01:17:34.875 --> 01:17:35.514
Pong.

647
01:17:36.075 --> 01:17:36.714
Pong.

648
01:17:37.715 --> 01:17:38.795
-Pong
-Let go!

649
01:17:38.994 --> 01:17:40.875
Let me go! Let me go!

650
01:17:41.595 --> 01:17:42.315
Pong!

651
01:17:42.394 --> 01:17:43.834
No! Get off! Get off!

652
01:17:47.994 --> 01:17:48.834
Panor!

653
01:17:49.155 --> 01:17:50.874
I'm sorry.

654
01:17:51.195 --> 01:17:52.834
Panor. Panor!

655
01:17:53.235 --> 01:17:54.594
I'm sorry.

656
01:17:55.114 --> 01:17:57.034
Calm down. calm down.

657
01:17:57.114 --> 01:17:59.115
The police are handling it now.

658
01:17:59.194 --> 01:18:01.674
My daughter is missing.
The hell is the police doing?!

659
01:18:02.034 --> 01:18:03.594
- And what about our daughters?
- Go find her.

660
01:18:03.674 --> 01:18:05.274
Calm down. Mr. Kieng.

661
01:18:05.354 --> 01:18:07.754
If anyone finds Jib and the other missing kids.

662
01:18:07.834 --> 01:18:09.154
the patrol will report it right away.

663
01:18:09.234 --> 01:18:10.954
And what are you sitting around? Go!

664
01:18:11.034 --> 01:18:13.314
Sir. there's a lot of work at the station.

665
01:18:13.714 --> 01:18:15.394
- What's going on?
- My child is missing!

666
01:18:18.154 --> 01:18:19.274
Missing children. Inspector.

667
01:18:34.433 --> 01:18:35.633
Panor! Panor!

668
01:18:36.833 --> 01:18:38.474
Please let me go. Panor. Please!

669
01:18:38.914 --> 01:18:39.914
I didn't mean to.

670
01:18:40.793 --> 01:18:41.914
Jib made me do it.

671
01:18:42.353 --> 01:18:43.313
Jib made me do it!

672
01:18:43.954 --> 01:18:45.034
I swear. Panor!

673
01:18:49.354 --> 01:18:51.233
I'm... I'm sorry.

674
01:18:52.833 --> 01:18:53.834
Please just let me go.

675
01:18:53.913 --> 01:18:55.394
Panor. please.

676
01:18:56.673 --> 01:18:58.514
Those legs you use for rattan ball.

677
01:19:00.434 --> 01:19:03.794
I don't think you'll be needing them anymore.

678
01:19:03.873 --> 01:19:04.833
No! No!

679
01:19:04.913 --> 01:19:05.873
No! No!

680
01:19:05.993 --> 01:19:06.993
No! Panor!

681
01:19:07.274 --> 01:19:07.994
No!

682
01:19:08.193 --> 01:19:08.834
Panor.

683
01:19:08.993 --> 01:19:10.953
Panor! Panor!

684
01:19:11.273 --> 01:19:12.913
No. no. Panor.

685
01:19:12.993 --> 01:19:14.313
Don't do this to me. Panor.

686
01:19:14.393 --> 01:19:15.193
Panor!

687
01:19:25.473 --> 01:19:26.233
Panor!

688
01:19:30.353 --> 01:19:30.993
Panor!

689
01:19:37.353 --> 01:19:38.073
Panor!

690
01:19:53.233 --> 01:19:54.592
Let's take a couple photo.

691
01:20:01.393 --> 01:20:04.153
One. two. three.

692
01:20:47.872 --> 01:20:48.752
Bind together...

693
01:20:49.632 --> 01:20:52.752
so you stay still for the photo.

694
01:20:59.552 --> 01:21:01.071
You make a lovely pair.

695
01:21:06.272 --> 01:21:07.232
Smile!

696
01:21:07.632 --> 01:21:10.071
One. two. three!

697
01:21:11.151 --> 01:21:12.192
There it is. Principal.

698
01:21:12.271 --> 01:21:13.632
The light is flickering. Principal.

699
01:21:15.072 --> 01:21:19.752
I'll process the order for a new light bulb.
and then you replace it

700
01:21:20.071 --> 01:21:20.832
Yes. sir.

701
01:21:20.952 --> 01:21:21.792
But...

702
01:21:23.511 --> 01:21:24.912
What's that smell?

703
01:21:25.671 --> 01:21:28.272
Didn't you take out the trash this evening?

704
01:21:28.992 --> 01:21:30.591
I did. sir. Took it out earlier.

705
01:21:30.672 --> 01:21:32.551
No idea where the smell is coming from.

706
01:21:32.631 --> 01:21:33.991
Then where could it be coming from?

707
01:21:35.511 --> 01:21:38.631
Why don't you open the room?

708
01:21:39.231 --> 01:21:39.871
Alright.

709
01:21:44.151 --> 01:21:45.431
I thought I locked it earlier.

710
01:21:46.391 --> 01:21:47.271
Did you forget?

711
01:21:49.951 --> 01:21:50.791
Janitor.

712
01:21:59.951 --> 01:22:01.670
Ghosts! Ghosts! Ghosts!

713
01:22:02.390 --> 01:22:02.990
Ghosts!

714
01:22:03.071 --> 01:22:03.551
Hey!

715
01:22:03.911 --> 01:22:04.790
"Bueng Prakan School"

716
01:22:04.871 --> 01:22:05.791
"National Children's Day 1985"

717
01:22:05.870 --> 01:22:06.710
"Unity. Discipline. Culture. Moral'"

718
01:22:09.991 --> 01:22:13.991
(Chanting)

719
01:22:15.031 --> 01:22:18.710
(Chanting)

720
01:22:24.431 --> 01:22:26.310
We've got six cases reported so far.

721
01:22:27.270 --> 01:22:28.031
Yes. sir.

722
01:22:28.670 --> 01:22:30.390
Three boys and three girls. sir.

723
01:22:32.231 --> 01:22:33.710
- Yes. sir.
- Police! Police!

724
01:22:34.751 --> 01:22:35.430
I'll call you back. sir.

725
01:22:35.510 --> 01:22:37.830
There's dead students at the school!

726
01:22:37.910 --> 01:22:38.750
What?

727
01:22:38.831 --> 01:22:41.550
Corporal. sergeant. to the school now! Go!

728
01:22:41.630 --> 01:22:42.350
Yes. sir!

729
01:22:42.431 --> 01:22:45.150
- Hurry up. follow them!
- Is it our child?

730
01:22:49.230 --> 01:22:50.710
Sergeant. follow me.

731
01:22:50.790 --> 01:22:51.470
Yes. sir.

732
01:23:40.150 --> 01:23:41.830
- Search everywhere. sarge.
- Yes. sir.

733
01:23:41.909 --> 01:23:42.989
What's going on. Inspector?

734
01:23:44.749 --> 01:23:45.670
Where's Panor?

735
01:23:46.510 --> 01:23:49.630
Four kids who had problems with Panor
were killed at the school.

736
01:23:53.590 --> 01:23:55.029
Inspector! Inspector!

737
01:23:55.349 --> 01:23:55.949
Inspector!

738
01:23:56.029 --> 01:23:57.469
Inspector! Inspector!

739
01:23:57.549 --> 01:23:58.429
What's going on. sarge?

740
01:24:01.069 --> 01:24:01.669
Shit!

741
01:24:42.588 --> 01:24:43.548
Inspector.

742
01:24:45.069 --> 01:24:45.748
What?

743
01:24:47.308 --> 01:24:47.988
Whoa.

744
01:24:52.828 --> 01:24:54.868
Inspector! Inspector!

745
01:24:55.468 --> 01:24:57.508
I found photos that could be... Argh!

746
01:24:59.949 --> 01:25:01.108
That's Uncle Tri!

747
01:25:06.788 --> 01:25:07.668
Who's that boy?

748
01:25:09.388 --> 01:25:11.068
Why are they so respectful of him?

749
01:25:14.108 --> 01:25:17.668
I believe these two were killed
because of Panor's vengeance.

750
01:25:20.388 --> 01:25:22.508
But with Tri. there might be another reason.

751
01:25:26.028 --> 01:25:27.428
I didn't kill Taew.

752
01:25:29.028 --> 01:25:30.827
I tried to save her.

753
01:25:31.547 --> 01:25:34.108
I think Tos definitely was cursed.

754
01:25:34.307 --> 01:25:36.988
Before he left. he said
he'd go fishing near Nuan's house.

755
01:25:38.267 --> 01:25:39.587
I've told you.

756
01:25:39.868 --> 01:25:41.668
That girl and her mother are into dark magic.

757
01:25:42.188 --> 01:25:44.188
Some black magic cults

758
01:25:44.267 --> 01:25:47.548
have a way to preserve their powers

759
01:25:47.627 --> 01:25:52.187
so the child born would inherit their magic.

760
01:25:53.667 --> 01:25:55.227
I think these photos

761
01:25:56.147 --> 01:25:57.867
have something to do with Panor.

762
01:26:13.107 --> 01:26:16.467
(Chanting)

763
01:26:16.867 --> 01:26:20.347
(Chanting)

764
01:26:20.547 --> 01:26:24.027
(Chanting)

765
01:26:24.347 --> 01:26:27.747
(Chanting)

766
01:26:34.427 --> 01:26:37.947
This year's "witching season"
will be intense. Principal.

767
01:26:38.467 --> 01:26:39.827
Here. take it.

768
01:26:40.067 --> 01:26:42.027
- Thank you. master.
- To protect yourself.

769
01:26:44.227 --> 01:26:47.187
Are you sure that Panor will come here?

770
01:26:48.187 --> 01:26:50.307
Alright. next.

771
01:26:50.386 --> 01:26:52.786
All the villagers have gathered here today.

772
01:26:52.867 --> 01:26:56.587
I believe Panor will come looking
for those with the tattoos.

773
01:26:57.706 --> 01:26:59.746
But how do we know which is which?

774
01:26:59.827 --> 01:27:00.867
There're so many people.

775
01:27:01.306 --> 01:27:03.067
Steamed fish curry. coming through!

776
01:27:03.146 --> 01:27:04.346
Steamed fish curry. coming through!

777
01:27:04.426 --> 01:27:05.186
Bring it here!

778
01:27:05.947 --> 01:27:06.787
Hello. teacher.

779
01:27:06.866 --> 01:27:07.786
Hello.

780
01:27:07.946 --> 01:27:09.866
How's Nid? Has he stopped drinking yet?

781
01:27:23.827 --> 01:27:26.666
- Where were you. Teacher Kwan?
- Getting food.

782
01:27:26.826 --> 01:27:28.986
This steamed fish curry is so delicious.

783
01:27:29.066 --> 01:27:31.306
If we don't quickly get some. it'll all be gone.

784
01:27:31.386 --> 01:27:33.146
Thank you so much.

785
01:27:33.426 --> 01:27:34.626
Let's eat together.

786
01:27:38.106 --> 01:27:40.546
- Thank you.
- Thank you. Have some water.

787
01:27:40.986 --> 01:27:43.666
I think I'll try the dessert first.
I have a sweet tooth.

788
01:27:58.866 --> 01:28:02.786
(Chanting)

789
01:28:03.386 --> 01:28:05.186
I'll cut. I'll slash

790
01:28:05.306 --> 01:28:07.185
And send evil spirits to torment

791
01:28:07.266 --> 01:28:09.666
Making it unbearable for you to stay

792
01:28:46.665 --> 01:28:47.705
What the hell is happening?

793
01:28:48.145 --> 01:28:49.025
I have no idea.

794
01:28:49.385 --> 01:28:50.625
They suddenly acted up.

795
01:28:51.065 --> 01:28:52.905
Someone must be behind this. Inspector.

796
01:28:56.345 --> 01:28:58.225
Panor is targeting those people.

797
01:28:58.665 --> 01:29:00.065
You must stop her.

798
01:29:00.145 --> 01:29:01.625
Don't let her cause more harm.

799
01:29:01.825 --> 01:29:02.465
Go.

800
01:29:14.504 --> 01:29:16.145
Hey. enough! What are you doing?

801
01:29:16.225 --> 01:29:17.065
Inspector!

802
01:29:18.065 --> 01:29:18.704
Stop!

803
01:29:28.664 --> 01:29:29.304
Stop!

804
01:29:35.345 --> 01:29:41.384
(Chanting)

805
01:29:41.465 --> 01:29:44.744
(Chanting)

806
01:29:49.224 --> 01:29:54.584
(Chanting)

807
01:29:54.664 --> 01:29:58.744
(Chanting)

808
01:30:23.383 --> 01:30:27.703
(Chanting)

809
01:30:39.064 --> 01:30:43.343
(Chanting)

810
01:30:45.184 --> 01:30:47.023
Panor. will you stop?

811
01:30:49.504 --> 01:30:50.623
It's too late.

812
01:30:51.823 --> 01:30:53.063
Those I respected...

813
01:30:54.263 --> 01:30:56.263
turned out to be the ones
who hurt me from the start.

814
01:30:57.503 --> 01:30:59.103
They deserve to die.

815
01:31:00.103 --> 01:31:02.143
Don't hurt more people. Panor.

816
01:31:29.262 --> 01:31:31.103
(Chanting)

817
01:31:43.302 --> 01:31:44.022
Teacher?

818
01:31:52.102 --> 01:31:52.902
Stop!

819
01:32:00.262 --> 01:32:01.143
Come with me.

820
01:32:02.262 --> 01:32:04.822
and I'll spare this insolent boy's life.

821
01:32:06.303 --> 01:32:07.302
Run!

822
01:32:11.222 --> 01:32:11.942
No!

823
01:32:12.622 --> 01:32:13.422
No

824
01:32:14.542 --> 01:32:15.422
So?

825
01:32:18.382 --> 01:32:19.262
No!

826
01:32:20.342 --> 01:32:20.982
No!

827
01:32:28.542 --> 01:32:29.262
I give up.

828
01:32:30.862 --> 01:32:31.982
I give up.

829
01:32:33.701 --> 01:32:34.661
Let him go.

830
01:32:41.542 --> 01:32:42.742
Come on. let's go.

831
01:32:50.102 --> 01:32:51.862
Don't expect me to spare your life.

832
01:32:53.381 --> 01:32:54.941
Stop! Don't come any closer.

833
01:33:03.782 --> 01:33:04.581
Drop the knife!

834
01:33:17.701 --> 01:33:19.061
Abbot. please help Piak.

835
01:33:20.301 --> 01:33:23.421
Piak. don't die. Piak!

836
01:33:24.661 --> 01:33:26.901
Abbot. help my son. Hang on. son.

837
01:33:27.421 --> 01:33:28.701
Stay strong. Piak.

838
01:33:29.701 --> 01:33:31.501
Abbot. help him!

839
01:33:31.941 --> 01:33:34.581
Hang in there. Piak. Don't die.

840
01:33:35.781 --> 01:33:37.421
Abbot! Please help him!

841
01:33:39.541 --> 01:33:40.381
Hang in there.

842
01:33:41.901 --> 01:33:43.821
Abbot! Don't die. Piak.

843
01:33:43.900 --> 01:33:45.421
Piak. don't die.

844
01:33:45.700 --> 01:33:47.500
Piak. hang in there. Hang in there.

845
01:33:47.581 --> 01:33:49.981
Abbot! Abbot!

846
01:33:50.901 --> 01:33:51.541
